# Common Guidelines — Codex Kit
#
# Behavioral guidelines live in AGENTS.md (Think Before Coding, Simplicity First,
# Surgical Changes, Goal-Driven Execution, Verify Before Handing Off,
# Respect User-Owned Content).
#
# Codex rules are for command-level execution policy only.
# Add project-specific prefix_rule(...) entries here when you want to prompt,
# allow, or forbid concrete commands outside the sandbox.
#
# Example:
# prefix_rule(
#     pattern = ["git", "push", "--force"],
#     decision = "prompt",
#     justification = "Force-pushing should require explicit approval.",
#     match = ["git push --force"],
# )
